scenes.description: Nanashi Mumei introduces her 3D showcase hashtag and begins a tour of her 3D room, starting with a close-up that she quickly pulls back from.
Mumei shows off her shoes and outfit, asking the audience to take screenshots.
The tour continues with her accessories: a satchel, a lantern, and her signature dagger, ending with a close-up of her face.
Mumei brandishes her dagger playfully and then realizes she might have scared the 'babies' in the chat.
Mumei performs several rounds of 'peek-a-boo' to calm down the chat.
Mumei shows various items in her treehouse, including caffeine, an hourglass, and 'the first friend'.
Mumei shows her fireplace and the berry tree growing right above it.
Mumei shows her desk with a map, dice, and a compass.
Mumei shows her bookshelf with various titled books and a brief glimpse of her bedroom area.
Mumei shows the view of the mountains from her balcony.
Mumei concludes the treehouse tour and is interrupted by 'Friend' floating into the scene.
